description: Run PL/SQL on Mobile and NoSQL DBs
overview:
Metatranz LLC is committed to bringing the power and convenience of big-database tools to the Mobile and NoSQL database world by using innovative techniques and latest technology.

Metatranz launch product ‘StepSqlite’ is a multi-target, optimizing, zero-maintenance PL/SQL compiler for the popular small database SQLite. It helps companies save time&money to go mobile with their existing PL/SQL code base.
